"version": "1.0.2",
"title": "8252: faithfulness, in human relationships",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "8252: faithfulness, in human relationships",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>Loyalty and commitment within human relationships is important in the life of God's people. It is seen particularly in fidelity within marriage, fulfilling family obligations, honouring vows, dutiful service and trustworthy speech and conduct.</p>\n<h2>Faithfulness within society</h2>\n<h3>It is important in the life of God's people</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hos12:6\">HOS 12:6</a></strong> <em>The word translated “love” is the Hebrew word “hesed”, which here expresses the loyalty and faithfulness that should characterise the life of God's people.</em> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mic6:8\">MIC 6:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt23:23\">MAT 23:23</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke11:42\">LUK 11:42</a></p>\n<h3>It is a reflection of God's faithfulness to his people</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps89:14\">PSA 89:14</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut32:4\">DEU 32:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa11:4-Isa11:5\">ISA 11:4–11:5</a></p>\n<h2>Faithfulness in marriage</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb13:4\">HEB 13:4</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mal2:11\">MAL 2:11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mal2:14-Mal2:15\">MAL 2:14–2:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt5:27-Matt5:28\">MAT 5:27–5:28</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod20:14\">EXO 20:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph5:33\">EPH 5:33</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Tim5:9\">1TI 5:9</a></p>\n<h2>Faithfulness in family relationships</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Tim5:4\">1TI 5:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Tim5:8\">1TI 5:8</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen24:47-Gen24:51\">GEN 24:47–24:51</a> <em>fulfilling family obligations in marriage arrangements</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen47:28-Gen47:31\">GEN 47:28–47:31</a> <em>fulfilling family obligations regarding burial</em><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ruth1:16-Ruth1:18\">RUT 1:16–1:18</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ruth2:11-Ruth2:12\">RUT 2:11–2:12</a>\n<a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam2:19\">1SA 2:19</a> <em>Hannah visits Samuel regularly.</em><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov31:15\">PRO 31:15</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov31:21\">PRO 31:21</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov31:27-Prov31:28\">PRO 31:27–31:28</a>\n<a href=\"https://ref.ly/John19:25-John19:27\">JHN 19:25–19:27</a> <em>Jesus Christ provides for his mother.</em></p>\n<h2>Faithfulness to vows and covenants</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num30:2\">NUM 30:2</a></strong> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen29:18\">GEN 29:18</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen29:30\">GEN 29:30</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen50:25\">GEN 50:25</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod13:19\">EXO 13:19</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Josh2:14\">JOS 2:14</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Josh6:25\">JOS 6:25</a>; \n<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Josh9:15-Josh9:20\">JOS 9:15–9:20</a> <em>Joshua and the Gibeonites</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam18:3\">1SA 18:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam20:8\">1SA 20:8</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam20:42\">1SA 20:42</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam23:16\">1SA 23:16</a>; \n<a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs20:34\">1KI 20:34</a> <em>Ben-Hadad and Ahab</em></p>\n<h2>Faithfulness in speech</h2>\n<h3>In carrying messages</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov13:17\">PRO 13:17</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov25:13\">PRO 25:13</a></p>\n<h3>In telling the truth</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov12:17\">PRO 12:17</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov14:5\">PRO 14:5</a></p>\n<h3>In bringing God's word</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer23:28\">JER 23:28</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor2:17\">2CO 2:17</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor4:2\">2CO 4:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Tim2:15\">2TI 2:15</a></p>\n<h2>Faithfulness in conduct</h2>\n<h3>In serving others</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/3John1:5\">3JN 1:5</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom16:1-Rom16:2\">ROM 16:1–16:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal6:10\">GAL 6:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet4:10\">1PE 4:10</a></p>\n<h3>In intercession</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom1:9-Rom1:10\">ROM 1:9–1:10</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph6:18\">EPH 6:18</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col4:2-Col4:4\">COL 4:2–4:4</a></p>\n<h3>In giving</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor8:7-2Cor8:11\">2CO 8:7–8:11</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr31:5-2Chr31:10\">2CH 31:5–31:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phil4:15-Phil4:18\">PHP 4:15–4:18</a></p>\n<h3>In handling money</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs12:13-2Kgs12:15\">2KI 12:13–12:15</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs22:7\">2KI 22:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr31:12-2Chr31:15\">2CH 31:12–31:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt25:21\">MAT 25:21</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke16:10\">LUK 16:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke19:17\">LUK 19:17</a></p>\n<h2>The rarity of true faithfulness</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov20:6\">PRO 20:6</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps12:1-Ps12:2\">PSA 12:1–12:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa57:1\">ISA 57:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer17:9\">JER 17:9</a></p>",
